{"tid":544964,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"淫審處日薪800元請審裁委員","createTime":"2018-01-30T05:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T12:06:08.000Z","uid":98659,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"031672bc5cb1bdf5189e848bab1b3487ff1acb87","tid":544964,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"警隊一哥盧偉聰昨日表示，警方內部的審核追蹤（internal audit trail）機制揭發去年有逾百名警務人員，包括有高級警司，涉嫌在辦公時間以辦公室電腦瀏覽與工作無關的網頁，部分含色情成分或跟股票投資等有關，警方內部調查科已展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n打工仔上班瀏覽與工作無關含色情成分的網站或短片固然不對，不過，在辦公時間看色情片也可是工作的一部分，其中淫褻物品審裁處的審裁委員正是可以「奉旨」返工看色情片。<br />\n<br />\n屬於司法機構之一的淫褻物品審裁處，根據《淫褻及不雅物品管制條例》（第390章）第5條組成審裁委員小組，該審裁委員小組的成員是由終審法院首席法官委任，日薪800元，任期三年，並可再獲委任。<br />\n<br />\n須居住香港7年以上<br />\n通曉書面英文及中文<br />\n小學程度可申請<br />\n審裁委員小組成員來自社會各階層，由擁有大學程度到小學程度人士亦可報名申請，以確保審裁具代表性及符合社會道德標準，<br />\n<br />\n工作職責<br />\n<br />\n審裁成員的工作職責之一，就是審視各種刊物，包括影片、錄音、印刷品等，是否涉及淫褻或不雅成分。 而審裁處在裁定物品是否屬淫褻或不雅時，會考慮社會人士普遍接受的道德標準、以及物品整體產生的效果、發佈對象等，過程相當嚴謹。<br />\n<br />\n申請方法<br />\n<br />\n據商務及經濟發展局通訊及創意產業科網頁顯示，若想成為審裁成員，可填妥申請表格，詳情請按此。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1636302/%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E7%9D%87%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E7%89%87%E3%80%80%E6%B7%AB%E5%AF%A9%E8%99%95%E6%97%A5%E8%96%AA800%E5%85%83%E8%AB%8B%E5%AF%A9%E8%A3%81%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1636302%2F%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%259D%2587%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%2589%2587%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B7%25AB%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2596%25AA800%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%5B%2Furl&d=BfQSKVsVgyFtsp%2BxWUngPDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=dfa99785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1636302/%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E7%9D%87%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E7%89%87%E3%80%80%E6%B7%AB%E5%AF%A9%E8%99%95%E6%97%A5%E8%96%AA800%E5%85%83%E8%AB%8B%E5%AF%A9%E8%A3%81%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1[/url</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cedb.gov.hk/ccib/chi/film/oat.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cedb.gov.hk%2Fccib%2Fchi%2Ffilm%2Foat.htm&d=BfQSKVsVgyFtsp%2BxWUngPDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6c18bbce\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cedb.gov.hk/ccib/chi/film/oat.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n認真有冇人報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367cc9664c08413479d768159ca0b76eb8263af5","tid":544964,"uid":83097,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"岩晒成人台班雞蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b404bc8041a5f6fcd627a8813b0e8c8824b1c6f0","tid":544964,"uid":104699,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"淫審處女職員"},{"pid":"1ac9f345c71951ec248431648531af869be6c7b6","tid":544964,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"日日有工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e0f47b806b69596c6156270b15378db77bf57d","tid":544964,"uid":108090,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"小六畢業但係要通曉英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809c50032b28f4741eeaafcf8d684f7e84a13b35","tid":544964,"uid":127347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"Ok啵，有性趣"},{"pid":"c50431b1e08469d74963e39fdab0f337d025c646","tid":544964,"uid":164928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"上年報過 都無回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b89f8316fa0becc159031924ad57d3c3a318266","tid":544964,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講果到d片好低質<br />\n好多人睇睇